{"title_page": "Wanzia", "text_new": "{{Short description|Genus of spiders}}\n{{Speciesbox\n| taxon = Wanzia fako\n| authority = Griswold, 1998\n| parent_authority = Griswold, 1998<ref name=NMBE />\n}}\n\n'''''Wanzia''''' is a [[monotypic taxon|monotypic]] [[genus]] of [[Central Africa]]n [[Araneomorphae|araneomorph]] spiders in the family [[Cyatholipidae]] containing the single species, '''''Wanzia fako'''''. It was first described by C. E. Griswold in 1998,<ref name=Gris1998>{{cite journal| last=Griswold| first=C. E.| year=1998| title=''Wanzia fako'', a new genus and species of spider from Cameroon (Araneae: Cyatholipidae).| journal=Entomologica Scandinavica| pages=121\u2013130| volume=29}}</ref> and has only been found in [[Cameroon]] and in [[Equatorial Guinea]].<ref name=NMBE>{{cite web| title=Gen. Wanzia Griswold, 1998| website=World Spider Catalog Version 20.0| accessdate=2019-05-30| year=2019| publisher=Natural History Museum Bern| url=http://www.wsc.nmbe.ch/genus/679| doi=10.24436/2}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q18093799|from2=Q2777959}}\n\n[[Category:Cyatholipidae]]\n[[Category:Monotypic Araneomorphae genera]]\n[[Category:Spiders described in 1998]]\n[[Category:Spiders of Africa]]\n\n\n{{Araneomorphae-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Short description|Genus of spiders}}\n{{Speciesbox\n| taxon = Wanzia fako\n| authority = Griswold, 1998\n| parent_authority = Griswold, 1998<ref name=NMBE />\n}}\n\n'''''Wanzia''''' is a [[monotypic taxon|monotypic]] [[genus]] of [[Central Africa]]n [[Araneomorphae|araneomorph]] spiders in the [[Cyatholipidae]] family containing the single species, '''''Wanzia fako'''''. It was first described by C. E. Griswold in 1998,<ref name=Gris1998>{{cite journal| last=Griswold| first=C. E.| year=1998| title=''Wanzia fako'', a new genus and species of spider from Cameroon (Araneae: Cyatholipidae).| journal=Entomologica Scandinavica| pages=121\u2013130| volume=29}}</ref> and has only been found in [[Cameroon]] and in [[Equatorial Guinea]].<ref name=NMBE>{{cite web| title=Gen. Wanzia Griswold, 1998| website=World Spider Catalog Version 20.0| accessdate=2019-05-30| year=2019| publisher=Natural History Museum Bern| url=http://www.wsc.nmbe.ch/genus/679| doi=10.24436/2}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Taxonbar|from=Q18093799|from2=Q2777959}}\n\n[[Category:Cyatholipidae]]\n[[Category:Monotypic Araneomorphae genera]]\n[[Category:Spiders described in 1998]]\n[[Category:Spiders of Africa]]\n\n\n{{Araneomorphae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wanzia"}
